# Git Branching 🌿

## Commands
git branch              # see branches
git branch new-feature  # create
git checkout new-feature # switch
git checkout -b new-feature # create+switch
git merge new-feature   # merge
git branch -d new-feature # delete

## Simple Flow
main branch    → live code
feature branch → new work

## Steps
1. Create branch
2. Write code
3. Merge to main
4. Delete branch
